Body:
orientation = Orientation(front, top)
assert orientation.get_side_rotation() == rotation
pytest.mark.parametrize('front, top, rotation', [(F, T, 0), (F, R, 1), (F,
    D, 2), (F, L, 3), (R, T, 0), (R, B, 1), (R, D, 2), (R, F, 3), (B, T, 0),
    (B, L, 1), (B, D, 2), (B, R, 3), (L, T, 0), (L, F, 1), (L, D, 2), (L, B,
    3), (T, B, 0), (T, R, 1), (T, F, 2), (T, L, 3), (D, L, 0), (D, F, 1), (
    D, R, 2), (D, B, 3)])
